This repository documents the architecture and research methodology of a
proprietary systematic-trading research platform ("MG Engine"). The full
engine source code is private and is NOT licensed for use, copying, modification,
or redistribution.

The documentation contained in this repository (README, docs/, diagrams) may be
read and referenced for the purpose of evaluating the author's work. No other
rights are granted.

Representative source modules and a deeper technical walk-through are available
on request.
